  "name": "Droskar",
  "content": "<p></p><h1 class=\"title\"><img src=\"http://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px\" title=\"PFS Legal\" /> Droskar</h1><h2><b>The Dark Smith</b></h2><b>Source</b> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy94wj?Pathfinder-Campaign-Setting-Inner-Sea-Gods-Hardcover\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Inner Sea Gods pg. 320</i></a><br /><b>Pathfinder Wiki</b> <a href=\"http://www.pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Droskar\">Droskar</a><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Details</h3><p><b>Alignment</b> NE<br /><b>Pantheon</b> Dwarven Deities<br /><b>Areas of Concern</b> Cheating, slavery, toil<br /><b>Domains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Artifice\">Artifice</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Charm\">Charm</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Darkness\">Darkness</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Evil\">Evil</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Trickery\">Trickery</a><br /><b>Subdomains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Artifice\">Construct</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Evil\">Daemon</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Trickery\">Deception</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Trickery\">Espionage (Trickery)</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Darkness\">Loss</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Trickery\">Thievery</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Artifice\">Toil</a><br /><i>* Requires the <u><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Acolyte%20of%20Apocrypha\">Acolyte of Apocrypha</a></u> trait.</i><br /><b>Favored Weapon</b> Light hammer<br /><b>Symbol</b> Fire under stone arch<br /><b>Sacred Animal(s)</b> Beetle<br /><b>Sacred Color(s)</b> Gray, orange<br /></p><h2 class=\"title\">For Followers of Droskar</h2><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Armor</h3><p><a href=\"MagicArmorDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Toiler's Armor\">Toiler's Armor</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Rings</h3><p><a href=\"MagicRingsDisplay.aspx?FinalName=Droskar's Guiding Ring\">Droskar's Guiding Ring</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Wondrous Items</h3><p><a href=\"MagicWondrousDisplay.aspx?FinalName=Gray Gambler's Hat\">Gray Gambler's Hat</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Traits</h3><p><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Extended Toil\">Extended Toil</a>, <a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Resigned\">Resigned</a>, <a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Toilcrafter\">Toilcrafter</a><br /><br /></p><div style=\"position:relative;left:0%;border:2px ridge #434343;width:100%;height:100%\"><div class=\"wiki-content-full\"><iframe style=\"overflow-y:hidden;width:100%;height:450px\" src=\"https://pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Droskar\"> </iframe></div>\n </div>",
